  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/c8580aa22a8dac0ad96d77ffec997c69.avif?t=1746881255\" width=614 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Content Creation & Streaming Guide]</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please include an introduction to the game in your created content.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please attach the game's store page link in the description, etc. (optional)</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Overview</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have opened a new hair salon. As a salon designer, welcome customers and cut their hair. And stop the villains who interfere with your business.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy multiplayer with friends for up to 4 players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/ae47d8535daf781ef9189632926453c3.webp?t=1746881255\" width=614 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/501b48397f2ac6ee11cda051bf69818b.poster.avif?t=1746881255\" width=614 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/501b48397f2ac6ee11cda051bf69818b.webm?t=1746881255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/501b48397f2ac6ee11cda051bf69818b.mp4?t=1746881255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customers with ridiculous hairstyles visit every day. Cut their hair refreshingly and earn money.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/b3d3de77f09be936b967fe4c044a17b9.webp?t=1746881255\" width=614 height=60 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/ac93d3233830b91ca4bd41efa1e4f38a.avif?t=1746881255\" width=614 height=354 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must survive by running a hair salon in a chaotic town. Survive among strange customers and the threat of the mafia!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/820c1942f6a684cb4f26c71225793337.webp?t=1746881255\" width=614 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/2a84faee545a1f0877010ac98c9d73c4.avif?t=1746881255\" width=614 height=354 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your salon, install furniture, and create the store you want.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automate annoying tasks to gain more free time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/c8580aa22a8dac0ad96d77ffec997c69.avif?t=1746881255\" width=614 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Content Creation & Streaming Guide]</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please include an introduction to the game in your created content.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please attach the game's store page link in the description, etc. (optional)</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Overview</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have opened a new hair salon. As a salon designer, welcome customers and cut their hair. And stop the villains who interfere with your business.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy multiplayer with friends for up to 4 players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/ae47d8535daf781ef9189632926453c3.webp?t=1746881255\" width=614 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/501b48397f2ac6ee11cda051bf69818b.poster.avif?t=1746881255\" width=614 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/501b48397f2ac6ee11cda051bf69818b.webm?t=1746881255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/501b48397f2ac6ee11cda051bf69818b.mp4?t=1746881255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customers with ridiculous hairstyles visit every day. Cut their hair refreshingly and earn money.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/b3d3de77f09be936b967fe4c044a17b9.webp?t=1746881255\" width=614 height=60 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/ac93d3233830b91ca4bd41efa1e4f38a.avif?t=1746881255\" width=614 height=354 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must survive by running a hair salon in a chaotic town. Survive among strange customers and the threat of the mafia!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/820c1942f6a684cb4f26c71225793337.webp?t=1746881255\" width=614 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398870/extras/2a84faee545a1f0877010ac98c9d73c4.avif?t=1746881255\" width=614 height=354 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your salon, install furniture, and create the store you want.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automate annoying tasks to gain more free time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
